<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>406</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lalpa ka Pathien,
 Chi tin nam tin chungah;
 Na lungsietna, vangsakna leh vangphat
 Na'n phungbang Na vuk hi.

[V2]
 Ka kipak mah mah ui,
 Na vangsakna chungah;
 Na Sapchuomte leh na nasemte hin,
 Na min pak bang chawi kau.

[V3]
 2. Pakchawih un chawihawih un,
 Nungak, tangvalte haw;
 Nupi, upa, atek-akhang tenle,
 Pathien chawian hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa paktil bangin,
 Chawi chimlo hiel dingin;
 I Aw teu leh I lungthim cheng cheng teu,
 Amah pie chiet hitiu.

[V5]
 4. Tichun I sepnau leh,
 I thilpiek sunteu chuh;
 I pau Pathien kawmah go thilpha chuh,
 I khawl uh hi zaw'n a.</lyrics>
<title>OH LORD, THY GRACIOUS GIFTS</title>
</song>